from sklearn.linear_model import Lasso
from sklearn.model_selection import cross_val_score
lasso_model = Lasso(alpha=0.1)
alphas = np.logspace(-5, 2,200)
# 执行10折交只验证并计草得分alphas = np.logspace(-5, 2,200)# 生成一系列aloha值
scores =[]
mse_scores =[]
# 构造空列表，用于存储模型的偏回归系数
lasso_cofficients = []
mse_values = []
for alpha in alphas:
    lasso_model.alpha = alpha
    lasso = Lasso(alpha = alpha, normalize=True, max_iter=10000)
    cv_scores = cross_val_score(lasso_model,X,y, cv=10)
    scores.append(cv_scores.mean())
    lasso.fit(X, y)
    lasso_cofficients.append(lasso.coef_)
    mse_scores.append(cv_scores.mean())#找到具有最高交只验证分数的最佳alpha值
    
    y_pred = lasso.predict(X)
    mse = mean_squared_error(y, y_pred)
    mse_values.append(mse)
best_alpha = alphas[np.argmax(scores)]
print(f"最佳alpha值 : {best_alpha}")

最佳alpha值 : 0.0019338917504552302

In [24]:
def get_confidences(pre_df, y):
    # 设置bootstrap重采样的次数
    n_bootstrap = 1000

    Confidences = []

    for item in [xgb.predict_proba(pre_df), 
                 knn.predict_proba(pre_df),
                 svm.predict_proba(pre_df),
                 lr.predict_proba(pre_df),
                 mlp.predict_proba(pre_df),
                 rfc.predict_proba(pre_df),
                 ada.predict_proba(pre_df),
                 gnb.predict_proba(pre_df),
                 cnb.predict_proba(pre_df)]:
        # 创建一个空数组，用于存储每个bootstrap样本的AUC值
        auc_values = np.empty(n_bootstrap)
        # 执行bootstrap重采样和AUC计算
        for i in range(n_bootstrap):
            # 从原始数据中进行有放回抽样
            indices = np.random.choice(len(y), size=len(y), replace=True)
            y_true_bootstrap = y.values[indices]
            y_pred_bootstrap = item[:, 1][indices]

            # 计算每个bootstrap样本的AUC值
            auc_values[i] = roc_auc_score(y_true_bootstrap, y_pred_bootstrap)

        # 计算置信区间的上下限
        lower = np.percentile(auc_values, 2.5)
        upper = np.percentile(auc_values, 97.5)
        Confidences.append((lower, upper))
    return Confidences

def roc_plot(flag, pre_df, y, conf):
    sns.set_palette("Set2")
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 10))
    roc_auc_lis = []

        roc_auc = auc(fpr, tpr)
        roc_auc_lis.append(roc_auc)
        plt.plot(fpr, tpr, label='AUC ({} = {} %95CI ({}-{}))'.format(model_names[inx], 
                                                                      round(roc_auc, 3), 
                                                                      round(conf[inx][0], 3),

    plt.plot([0, 1], [0, 1], 'k--', lw=2)

    plt.ylim([-0.05, 1.05])
    plt.xticks(size=14)

    plt.xlabel('False Positive Rate', fontsize=18)
    plt.ylabel('True Positive Rate', fontsize=18)
    plt.title('{} ROC Curve'.format(flag), color='r', fontsize=22)
    plt.legend(loc="lower right", fontsize=16)
    plt.show()

def eval_model(pre_df, y, auc_lis):
    df_ = []
    model_names = ["XGBoost", "KNN", "SVM", "Logistic", "MLP", "RandomForest", "AdaBoost", "GNB", "CNB"]
    for inx, pred in enumerate([xgb.predict_proba(pre_df), 
                                knn.predict_proba(pre_df),
                                svm.predict_proba(pre_df),
                                lr.predict_proba(pre_df),
                                mlp.predict_proba(pre_df),
                                rfc.predict_proba(pre_df),
                                ada.predict_proba(pre_df),
                                gnb.predict_proba(pre_df),
                                cnb.predict_proba(pre_df)]): 
        cm = confusion_matrix(y, pred.argmax(axis=1))
        # 从混淆矩阵中提取真阳性、假阴性、假阳性和真阴性
        tn, fp, fn, tp = cm.ravel()
        # 计算特异性（Specificity）
        specificity = tn / (tn + fp)
        df_.append([auc_lis[inx], accuracy_score(y, pred.argmax(axis=1)), recall_score(y, pred.argmax(axis=1)), specificity, 
                       (recall_score(y, pred.argmax(axis=1))+specificity)/2, f1_score(y, pred.argmax(axis=1))])
    res_df = pd.DataFrame(df_, index=model_names, columns=["AUC", "Accuracy", "Sensitivity", "Specificity", "Youden Index", "F1 score"])
    return res_df

def decision_curve(sign, pre_df, Y):
    plt.figure(figsize=(12,12))
    flag = 0
    for inx, pred in enumerate([xgb.predict_proba(pre_df), 
                                knn.predict_proba(pre_df),
                                svm.predict_proba(pre_df),
                                lr.predict_proba(pre_df),
                                mlp.predict_proba(pre_df),
                                rfc.predict_proba(pre_df),
                                ada.predict_proba(pre_df),
                                gnb.predict_proba(pre_df),
                                cnb.predict_proba(pre_df)]):
        pt_arr = []
        net_bnf_arr = []
        jiduan = []
        pred_ans = pred[:, 1].ravel()
        for i in range(0,100,1):
            pt = i /100
            #compiute TP FP
            pred_ans_clip = np.zeros(pred_ans.shape[0])
            for j in range(pred_ans.shape[0]):
                if pred_ans[j] >= pt:
                    pred_ans_clip[j] = 1
                else:
                    pred_ans_clip[j] = 0
                TP = np.sum((Y) * np.round(pred_ans_clip))
                FP = np.sum((1 - Y) * np.round(pred_ans_clip))
            net_bnf = ( TP-(FP * pt/(1-pt)) )/Y.shape[0]
            # print('pt {}, TP {}, FP {}, net_bf {}'.format(pt,TP,FP,net_bnf))
            pt_arr.append(pt)
            net_bnf_arr.append(net_bnf)
            jiduan.append((sum(Y==1)-sum(Y==0)*pt/(1-pt))/len(Y))
        plt.plot(pt_arr, net_bnf_arr, lw=2, label='{}'.format(model_names[inx]))
        flag = np.min(net_bnf_arr)
        if np.min(net_bnf_arr) < flag:
            flag = np.min(net_bnf_arr)
    plt.plot(pt_arr, np.zeros(len(pt_arr)), color='k', lw=2, linestyle='dotted',label='None')
    plt.plot(pt_arr, jiduan , color='b', lw=2, linestyle='--',label='All')
    plt.xlim([0.0, 1.0])
    plt.ylim([float(flag), 0.35])
    plt.xticks(size=14)
    plt.yticks(size=14)
    plt.xlabel('Risk Threshold', size=18)
    plt.ylabel('Net Benefit', size=18)
    plt.title("{} Decision Curve".format(sign), color='r', size=20)
    plt.legend(loc="lower left", fontsize=16)
    plt.grid()
    plt.show()

from sklearn.calibration import calibration_curve

plt.figure(figsize=(10, 8))

for inx, probs in enumerate([xgb_pred, knn_pred, svm_pred, lr_pred, mlp_pred, rfc_pred, ada_pred, gnb_pred, cnb_pred]):
    # 计算校准曲线的相关指标
    fraction_of_positives, mean_predicted_value = calibration_curve(y_test, probs[:, 1], n_bins=10)

    # 计算校准值（最大误差）
    max_calibration_error = max(abs(fraction_of_positives - mean_predicted_value))
    
    # 绘制校准曲线
    plt.plot(mean_predicted_value, fraction_of_positives, lw=2, 
             label="{} ({:.3f})".format(model_names[inx], max_calibration_error))

# 绘制完美的校准曲线
plt.plot([0, 1], [0, 1], "k:", label="Perfectly calibrated")

plt.xlabel("Mean Predicted Value", size=18)
plt.ylabel("Fraction of Positives", size=18)
plt.xticks(size=14)
plt.yticks(size=14)
plt.ylim([-0.05, 1.05])

plt.legend(loc="upper left", fontsize=15)
plt.show()
